  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "Cook the fideua according to package instructions until al dente.",
    "Chop the minari into small pieces and set aside.",
    "In a large pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, black pepper, and chilli flakes to the pan, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the cooked fideua to the pan and stir to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Add the chopped minari to the pan and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes until slightly tender.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and top with sliced almonds.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 10-12 minutes, or until the top is golden brown and crispy."
